{
  "name": "{{SERVICE_DISPLAY_NAME}}",
  "host": "{{NG_RECORD}}",
  "port": 443,
  "protocol": "https",
  "paths": [
    {
      "incoming": "{{INCOMING_PATH}}",
      "outgoing": "{{OUTGOING_PATH}}"
    }
  ]
}

{{!--
SmartGateway (Kong) route configuration for external-facing APIs.
Only needed when DNS discovery confirmed external internet traffic through SmartGateway.
NOT needed for brand domains used internally only.

CRITICAL:
  - host MUST be the NG-record (not E-record)
  - port MUST be 443
  - protocol MUST be "https"

Placeholders:
  {{SERVICE_DISPLAY_NAME}}  — human-readable service name for the route
  {{NG_RECORD}}             — NG-record: {APP_NAME}.{PROJECT_ID}.{ENV_TYPE}.jet-internal.com
  {{INCOMING_PATH}}         — external path (e.g., "/api/v1/partners")
  {{OUTGOING_PATH}}         — internal path (e.g., "/api/v1/partners")

Review channel: #help-http-integrations
--}}
